<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p>I need a little help. I often drag elements and tabs accidentally with my touchpad, so I figured out, that I can change that using the synaptics option &quot;<strong>TapAndDragGesture&quot;</strong> and set it to false.</p> <p>I did that, however, it doesnt seem to work.</p> <p>Other options work perfectly, so I know the config file is read.</p> <p>&#x200B;</p> <p>If I check via libinput list-devices, I get this entry:</p> <pre><code>Device: SYNA8004:00 06CB:CD8B Touchpad Kernel: /dev/input/event9 Group: 9 Seat: seat0, default Size: 97x53mm Capabilities: pointer gesture Tap-to-click: disabled Tap-and-drag: enabled Tap drag lock: disabled Left-handed: disabled Nat.scrolling: disabled Middle emulation: disabled Calibration: n/a Scroll methods: *two-finger edge Click methods: *button-areas clickfinger Disable-w-typing: enabled Disable-w-trackpointing: enabled Accel profiles: flat *adaptive custom Rotation: n/a </code></pre> <p>So it still seems to be enabled. </p> <p>My .config at /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d looks like this:</p> <pre><code>Section &quot;InputClass&quot; Identifier &quot;touchpad&quot; Driver &quot;libinput&quot; MatchIsTouchpad &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;Tapping&quot; &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;NaturalScrolling&quot; &quot;true&quot; Option &quot;TapButton1&quot; &quot;1&quot; Option &quot;TapButton2&quot; &quot;3&quot; Option &quot;TapButton3&quot; &quot;2&quot; Option &quot;VertEdgeScroll&quot; &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;VertTwoFingerScroll&quot; &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;HorizEdgeScroll&quot; &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;HorizTwoFingerScroll&quot; &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;CircularScrolling&quot; &quot;on&quot; Option &quot;CircScrollTrigger&quot; &quot;2&quot; Option &quot;EmulateTwoFingerMinZ&quot; &quot;40&quot; Option &quot;EmulateTwoFingerMinW&quot; &quot;8&quot; Option &quot;CoastingSpeed&quot; &quot;0&quot; Option &quot;FingerLow&quot; &quot;30&quot; Option &quot;FingerHigh&quot; &quot;50&quot; Option &quot;MaxTapTime&quot; &quot;125&quot; Option &quot;TapAndDragGesture&quot; &quot;false&quot; EndSection </code></pre> <p>Any Ideas what I did wrong?</p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/handgemenge4"> /u/handgemenge4 </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/archlinux/comments/13j4gw6/tap_and_drag_not_working_tapanddraggesture/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/archlinux/comments/13j4gw6/tap_and_drag_not_working_tapanddraggesture/">[comments]</a></span>